						<h1>
															Getting Started Guide: FTP									</h1>
			
																
				
					<div style='font-size:12px; color:#aaa; margin-bottom:-10px; padding-top:5px;'>
							<div style='float:left; margin-right:20px;'><span style='color:#606060;'>Written by </span><a href='https://plus.google.com/102670474114655224886?rel=author'>Brad Markle</a></div>
							<div style='float:left; margin-right:20px;'><span style='color:#606060;'>Views:</span> <span name='page_views' id='page_views'>144,554</span></div>
							<div style='float:left; margin-right:20px;' title='Originally published: Aug 25, 2011'><span style='color:#606060;'>Published:</span> Apr 21, 2016</div>
							<div style='float:left; margin-right:20px;'><span style='color:#606060;'>Comments:</span> <a href='#comments'>62</a></div>
